### N3-ALL THINGS PRAISE THEE 

 **1**   
 Ade nyinaa yi W'ayε;   
 S'ro, asase, po ne wim,   
 Woyεε wɔn maa W'anuonyam,   
 Wɔkyerε Wo kεseyε   
 Ka sε obiara nsom Wo;   
 Ma yεn nso yenyi W'ayε. 

 **2**   
 Ade nyinaa yi W'ayε;   
 Sum to hann nnwom anadwo;   
 Ade nyinaa yi W'ayε,   
 Hann  to Wo tumi ho dwom;   
 B're ne beae reyi W'ayε,   
 Ma yεn nso yenyi W'ayε. 

 **3**   
 Ade nyinaa yi W'ayε   
 N-su bosu, nyankontɔn,   
 O-wi-a ne munumkum;   
 ‘Suten, ahum, ahoh'ru   
 Ne awɔw hyε W'anuonyam;   
 Ma yεn nso nhyε W'anuonyam. 

 **4**   
 Ade nyinaa yi W'ayε;   
 Ɔbɔadeε, Asεm tumfo,   
 Awɔ-mmaa-nyinaa Honhom,   
 Yεkoto Wo nan ase,   
 Ma yεn koma so ma Wo;   
 Ma yεn nso yenyi W'ayε.

### N34-Go Labour On 

 **1**   
 Fa w'ahoɔden ny'naa yε ‘dwuma   
 Fa ‘nigye yε w'Agya ‘pεde;   
 Ɛyε kwan a ‘W'ra no faa so;   
 Ɛnsε sε Nakoa fa so bi? 

 **2**   
 Yε adwuma; woremm'rε ngu   
 Fam adehw'rew yε s'ro mfaso:   
 Sε nnipa ntiew', nnɔw', nyiw ayέ a   
 ‘W'ra n' bεkamfo', nnipa yε dεn? 

 **3**   
 ‘Dekye wɔ hɔ yi yε ‘dwuma;   
 Wiase ‘nadwo sum reba ntεm;   
 Yε w'dwuma ɔhare so;   
 Wɔmfa anihaw nnye akra. 

 **4**   
 Kɔ so, ntɔ beraw, wɔn bɔ mpae;   
 Yε ‘badwemma, gye akra nkwa;   
 Fi adi kɔ wiase mm'rɔn so,   
 Hyε wɔn a wɔafom kwan bra fie. 

 **5**   
 Ma w'ani nnye w'adwuma yεm';   
 Ɛbrε akyi wɔ ɔhome;   
 Wobεte Ayef'rokum' nne   
 Ɛdasu mu sε, “Hwε Maba!”

### N39-What can wash away my sin? 

 **1**   
 Dεn na εpa me bɔne?   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya;   
 Dεn na εma me mu tew?   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya; 

 **Nnyeso:**   
 Mogya a εhoa me   
 Ho no bo yε den sɔ;   
 Minnim nsuti fof'ro,   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya. 

 **2**   
 Nea εfa m'ahotew   ho –   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya;   
 Ma fafiri no ho nso –   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya; 

 **3**   
 Hwee ntumi mpata bɔne –   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya;   
 Me papayε rentumi –   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya; 

 **4**   
 Mεto anuonyam dwom sε –   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya;   
 Eyi nti m'ayeyi ni –   
 Minhu hwee sε Yesu mogya;
